---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Your Name" description="Designer with 7 years at Shopify, based in Tokyo.">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="about-bio">
      <p>
        I'm a product designer with seven years at Shopify, where I joined as a design intern and grew into a
        senior role on the fulfillment and commerce infrastructure teams. Over that time I worked across merchant-facing
        tooling, internal operational systems, and consumer-side checkout experiences — mostly in the part of the
        product where business logic is complex and the stakes for getting it wrong are high.
      </p>
      <p>
        I care most about the moments where design has to carry a lot of cognitive weight: helping someone make a
        decision they can't undo, navigate a system too large to hold in their head at once, or trust that something
        invisible is working correctly. That's where I think the craft matters most.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm based in Tokyo. I moved there in 2020 and have been working remotely since. Outside of work I study
        Japanese, run, and occasionally build small web tools to scratch my own itches.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm currently looking for new opportunities — senior or staff-level product design roles at companies
        building tools for professionals or complex workflows. If that sounds like you, I'd like to hear from you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-details">
      <div class="detail-group">
        <h3>Experience</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Senior Product Designer, Shopify — 2020–2024</li>
          <li>Product Designer, Shopify — 2018–2020</li>
          <li>Design Intern, Shopify — 2017</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-group">
        <h3>Based in</h3>
        <p>Tokyo, Japan</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-contact">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        The best way to reach me is by email:
        <a href="mailto:hello@yourname.com">hello@yourname.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .container {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .about-bio {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .about-bio p {
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .about-details {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    padding-block: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .detail-group h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .detail-group ul {
    list-style: none;
  }
  .detail-group li,
  .detail-group p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  .about-contact h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .about-contact p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .about-contact a {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
